# To-Do List Application

A simple yet powerful to-do list application built with **Node.js**, **Advanced JavaScript (ES6+ features)**, **HTML**, and **CSS**. This app allows users to create, update, and delete tasks, making it easy to keep track of daily activities.

## Features
- **Add, Edit, and Delete Tasks**: Users can create new tasks, edit existing tasks, or delete tasks they no longer need.
- **Mark as Complete**: Tasks can be marked as completed and visually separated from pending tasks.
- **Persistent Storage**: Tasks are saved to a database, allowing users to retrieve their tasks even after closing the app.
- **Responsive Design**: Built to work seamlessly on various devices, from mobile to desktop.

## Getting Started
Follow these instructions to get a copy of the project up and running on your local machine for development and testing.

### Prerequisites
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (v14 or higher)
  
### Installation
1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/xolanisyav04/todo-list.git
   cd todo-list
